{{Infobox dungeon |name = Seafoam Islands |image = [[File:Seafoam Islands.png|400px]] |caption = An overhead map of the Seafoam Islands. |tokens = 1,250 |location = West of Cinnabar Island, on route 19. }} The '''Seafoam Islands''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Kanto]]. It has 25 tiles arranged in a 5x5 square, including 5 chest tiles, 13 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
